doctype html
html.no-js(lang='en-us')
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    title Myswyftpay - Coming Soon
    meta(name='description', content='The description should optimally be between 150-160 characters.')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    meta(name='author', content='ThemeHelite')
    link(rel='shortcut icon', href='favicon.ico')
    link(rel='apple-touch-icon', sizes='144x144', href='public/img/favicon-retina-ipad.png')
    link(rel='apple-touch-icon', sizes='114x114', href='public/img/favicon-retina-iphone.png')
    link(rel='apple-touch-icon', sizes='72x72', href='public/img/favicon-standard-ipad.png')
    link(rel='apple-touch-icon', sizes='57x57', href='public/img/favicon-standard-iphone.png')
    link(rel='stylesheet', type='text/css', href='public/css/style.css')
  body
    #loading
      #preloader.animated-middle.flipInY
        img.loading-logo(src='public/img/logo.png', alt='')
        |  
        span.loading-text Loading 
        span.load
          span.loading-dot
          span.loading-dot
          span.loading-dot
          span.loading-dot
    #fullpage
      #section0.section
        img.home-logo(src='public/img/logo.png', alt='')
        .slideshow-home
        .slide-overlay
        .intro
          #clock.container.open-anim.opacity-0
          p.open-anim.opacity-0
            | Before the launch, enjoy a 
            strong Very Limited Opportunity
            |  by subscribing to our newsletter.
            br
            |  Click on the next button to get more information about our platform.
          |  
          a#button-more.light-btn.open-anim.opacity-0 More Information
        .scroll-indicator
          a#indicator-scroll
            i.icon.ion-ios-arrow-down
      #section1.section
        section#about.text-left-block
          .row.row-no-margin
            #invert-slideshow.col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6.slideshow-about.split-section.foo
            #invert-text.col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6.left-center-text.split-section
              .left-center-part.foo
                h2 About us
                p
                  | Myswyftpay int'l is a community of like-minded people all over the world who help each other.
                p
                  | It is an idea evolved to unite people to help each other financially in this unfair financial apocalypse. We believe that poverty is not lack of resources but lack of sharing and caring. We give you a basic platform which helps millions of participants worldwide to find those who need help and those who are ready to provide help at no cost.
                p
                  | We are a member to member donation exchange network. All funds donated directly to members are free will donations. The Community is designed to allow members to give financial help when they are able and to receive financial help when they need it. It is within this spirit that members participate in faith and unity towards helping their fellow members as often as possible.
                p
                  | We believe in participants helping each other to reach a common goal: ‘FINANCIAL FREEDOM’.
      #section2.section
        section#services.text-left-block
          .row.row-no-margin
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6.left-center-text.split-section.foo
              .left-center-part
                h2 How it works
                p
                  | We address the needs of our members through the discovery and application of unique Pairing Insights.
                #carousel-services.carousel.slide(data-interval='6000', data-ride='carousel')
                  ol.carousel-indicators
                    li.active(data-target='#carousel-services', data-slide-to='0')
                    li(data-target='#carousel-services', data-slide-to='1')
                    li(data-target='#carousel-services', data-slide-to='2')
                  .carousel-inner
                    .active.item
                      .row
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6.block-services
                          span.icon-services.icon.ion-android-call
                          h3 Mobile Number Verification
                          p
                            | A unique security code is sent to your mobile number to verify your identity.
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6.block-services
                          span.icon-services.icon.ion-ios-flask-outline
                          h3 Matching
                          p
                            | As a verified member, you will be matched to provide help to two other verified members just like you. This means that you will have to share the money into two equal parts and then send each part to one of the members. For instance, if you choose the basic package (#8358;20,000) you will have to pay #10,000 to one member and another &#8358;10,000 to the second member
                    .item
                      .row
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6.block-services
                          span.icon-services.icon.ion-ios-navigate-outline
                          h3 Confirmation
                          p
                            | You will then be required to upload the proof of your donation to each of the members so that they can confirm the receipt of your donation.
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6.block-services
                          span.icon-services.icon.ion-ios-pulse
                          h3 Donation and Benefit
                          p
                            | As soon as your donations have been confirmed by the recipients, you will be eligible to receive three donations from
                            | 3 different members just like you. And you will be matched to receive anytime between 24hrs to 1 week.
                  a.carousel-control.left(href='#carousel-services', data-slide='prev')
                    span.icon-prev
                  a.carousel-control.right(href='#carousel-services', data-slide='next')
                    span.icon-next
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6.slideshow-services.split-section.foo
      #section4.section
        section#contact.text-left-block
          .row.row-no-margin
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6.left-center-text.split-section.spec-padding-bottom.foo
              .left-center-part
                h2 Get in touch
                p.subtitle
                  | We are here to help you 
                  strong Tuesday through Saturday
                  | , from 9:00 AM to 10:00 PM.
                  br
                  |  Contact us via 
                  strong Phone :
                  |  
                  a.phone-mail-link(href='tel:0708-572-4967')  (+234) 708-572-4967
                  |  or 
                  strong Email
                  |  : 
                  a.phone-mail-link(href='mailto:support@myswyftpay.com') support@myswyftpay.com
                .row
                  .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-lg-12
                    form#contact-form(name='contact-form', method='POST', data-name='Contact Form')
                      .row
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-lg-12.display-none
                          .form-group
                            input#checking.form.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Leave this field empty', onfocus="this.placeholder=''", onblur="this.placeholder='Leave this field empty'", name='checking', data-name='Checking')
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6
                          .form-group
                            input#name.form.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Name*', onfocus="this.placeholder=''", onblur="this.placeholder='Name*'", name='name', data-name='Name', required='')
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6
                          .form-group
                            input#email.form.form-control(type='email', placeholder='Email Address*', onfocus="this.placeholder=''", onblur="this.placeholder='Email Address*'", name='email', data-name='Email Address', required='')
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6
                          .form-group
                            input#company.form.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Company name', onfocus="this.placeholder=''", onblur="this.placeholder='Company name'", name='company', data-name='Company', required='')
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6
                          .form-group
                            input#phone.form.form-control(type='tel', placeholder='Phone number*', onfocus="this.placeholder=''", onblur="this.placeholder='Phone number*'", name='phone', data-name='Phone', required='')
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-lg-12
                          .form-group
                            textarea#text-area.form.textarea.form-control(placeholder='Your message here*... 20 characters Min.', onfocus="this.placeholder=''", onblur="this.placeholder='Your message here*... 20 characters Min.'", name='message', data-name='Text Area', required='')
                          |  
                          span.sub-text * Required fields
                      |  
                      button#valid-form.btn.btn-color(type='submit') Send my Message
                    #block-answer
                      #answer
                p.copyright &copy; Myswyftpay - Made for Awesome People
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-6.map-info.split-section.foo
              #map
    #info
      button.close-newsletter
        i.icon.ion-close-round
      .content
        img.brand-logo(src='public/img/logo.png', alt='')
        p.subtitle
          | Sign up to the Myswyftpay News before our launching on the 19th of April.
        #subscribe
          form#notifyMe(action='php/notify-me-2.php', method='POST')
            .form-group
              .controls
                input#mail-sub.form-control.email.srequiredField(type='text', name='email', placeholder='Click here to write your email', onfocus="this.placeholder=''", onblur="this.placeholder='Click here to write your email'")
                i.fa.fa-spinner.opacity-0
                |  
                button.btn.btn-lg.submit Get notified
                .clear
      .block-message
        .message
          p.notify-valid
      p.spam-news
        i.fa.fa-lock
        |  We hate spam just as much as you do. Your email will stay secret.
    |  
    a#open-newsletter.action-btn Notify me
    #social-nav
      ul
        li
          a(href='https://www.facebook.com/myswyftpayng', target='_blank')
            i.fa.fa-facebook
        li
          a(href='https://twitter.com/myswyftpayint', target='_blank')
            i.fa.fa-twitter
        li
          a(href='https://instagram.com/myswyftpayintl', target='_blank')
            i.fa.fa-instagram
    .pswp(tabindex='-1', role='dialog', aria-hidden='true')
      .pswp__bg
      .pswp__scroll-wrap
        .pswp__container
          .pswp__item
          .pswp__item
          .pswp__item
        .pswp__ui.pswp__ui--hidden
          .pswp__top-bar
            .pswp__counter
            |  
            button.pswp__button.pswp__button--close(title='Close (Esc)')
            |  
            button.pswp__button.pswp__button--share(title='Share')
            |  
            button.pswp__button.pswp__button--fs(title='Toggle fullscreen')
            |  
            button.pswp__button.pswp__button--zoom(title='Zoom in/out')
            .pswp__preloader
              .pswp__preloader__icn
                .pswp__preloader__cut
                  .pswp__preloader__donut
          .pswp__share-modal.pswp__share-modal--hidden.pswp__single-tap
            .pswp__share-tooltip
          |  
          button.pswp__button.pswp__button--arrow--left(title='Previous (arrow left)')
          |  
          button.pswp__button.pswp__button--arrow--right(title='Next (arrow right)')
          .pswp__caption
            .pswp__caption__center
